    Retrieves the version information of available Netty artifacts.

    This class retrieves the version information from META-INF/io.netty5.versions.properties, which is generated in build time. Note that it may not be possible to retrieve the information completely, depending on your environment, such as the specified ClassLoader, the current SecurityManager.
